news.title: China's central bank to offer cheap loans to support builders' bonds: Sources
news.para: China has stepped up support in recent weeks for the property sector, a pillar accounting for a quarter of the world's second-biggest economy. Many developers defaulted on their debt obligations and were forced to halt construction.

news.title: Noida: YEIDA reclaims 6,500 acres from panchayat for industrial town
news.para: ​Under YEIDA's Master Plan Phase-2 for development around the Jewar airport, a Logistics Park is proposed to be built in the Tappal-Bajna Urban Center.

news.title: Pay rent for using municipal property or face action: Canacona civic body
news.para: Some councillors at the council meeting said the houses built illegally before 2018 should be regularised by giving house numbers, which they said will add revenue to the council.
